<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Shift Assigned</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
    <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #3498db;">Shift Assigned to You</h2>
        <p>Hello {{seekerName}},</p>
        <p>You have been assigned to a shift for the following job:</p>
        <div style="background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #3498db;">
            <p><strong>Job Title:</strong> {{jobTitle}}</p>
            <p><strong>Employer:</strong> {{providerName}}</p>
            <p><strong>Start Date:</strong> {{startDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>Start Time:</strong> {{startTime}}</p>
            <p><strong>End Date:</strong> {{endDate}}</p>
            <p><strong>End Time:</strong> {{endTime}}</p>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
        </div>
        <p>Please confirm your attendance and arrive on time. If you have any questions, contact the employer directly.</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br>WorkNow Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

